<p>Harold and Christine are planning a party. They decide they need 2 hamburgers and 3 pieces of fruit for each person. They make a chart so that they can know how many of each to buy depending on how many people show up. Then, while mixing lemonade, Harold spills some on their chart!</p>
        <p class='prompt'>Help Harold and Christine with their planning by filling in the missing numbers.</p>
